description:
Danny recaps the most recent Bachelorette episode, featuring the introduction of Spencer, a sit down with Clare & Dale, and a horse race. Then Danny welcomes Sasha Morfaw of @thebravobreakdown to talk about this week's Real Housewives of Potomac.


RHOP Recap: 18:20ish
